  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "The complete saga of the galaxy's most feared traitors, collecting the Night Lords trilogy — Soul Hunter, Blood Reaver and Void Stalker — alongside the short fiction that frames it. Follow Talos, prophet of a murdered Primarch, and his brothers of First Claw across ten thousand years of bitterness: from a black crusade against the forge world of Crythe, through a treacherous alliance with Huron Blackheart's Red Corsairs, to a final hunt on the haunted world of Tsagualsa where the Eldar move to end them. A study of damnation, brotherhood and the long shadow of betrayal, told entirely from the side of the damned.",
